{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01KcoRprGvqUvnWfgbUcAPVP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DR81h2TVGVecXprehMvBvc","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add src/ts/package.json src/ts/package-lock.json src/ts/src/binding.ts src/ts/src/errors.ts src/ts/src/validation.ts src/ts/src/index.ts && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfeat(11b): TS SDK calls fathomdb-napi via rethrowTyped envelope\n\nReplace the pure-TS Engine stub with thin wrappers over the napi-rs\nbinding. Every native call funnels through `intercept` /\n`interceptSync` which delegates to `rethrowTyped` on failure:\n`rethrowTyped` parses the JSON envelope the binding emits in\n`err.message`, looks up the FathomDbError leaf class by stable\ncode, and constructs it with the typed payload.\n\n- errors.ts: native FathomDbError hierarchy keeps `instanceof` chain\n  intact (napi-rs cannot throw a Rust-defined JS class). Adds two\n  amendment leaves (EmbedderNotConfiguredError under EmbedderError,\n  KindNotVectorIndexedError under VectorError) and FathomDbPanicError\n  (intentionally NOT a FathomDbError subclass, mirroring 11a).\n- binding.ts: hand-rolled loader using createRequire + a platform-\n  tagged .node lookup, sidestepping CJS/ESM friction with the\n  generated napi loader.\n- validation.ts: JS-side validateFfiString + deep tree walk to reject\n  embedded NUL and lone UTF-16 surrogates BEFORE napi-rs converts\n  the JS string and silently replaces surrogates with U+FFFD\n  (AC-068b would otherwise go undetected).\n- package.json: `napi build` driven via `--cargo-cwd` to point at\n  the workspace crate; debug build enables the `test-hooks` feature\n  so the AC-067 force-panic probe is reachable from tests.\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit TS package rewire"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":704,"cache_read_input_tokens":201865,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":704},"output_tokens":62,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d1c788b7-12bf-4bce-9fc4-3a0fdd43bef6","uuid":"139c0004-90f4-4cd8-bfab-95e81e27e90a"}
